"    Continuous Hormonal Treatment for Endometriosis:",
"   </p>",
"   <p>",
"    <a class=\"external\" href=\"file://www.youngwomenshealth.org/endo_cont_horm.html\">",
"     file://www.youngwomenshealth.org/endo_cont_horm.html",
"    </a>",
"   </p>",
